<br>
He does nothing, and covers his inaptitude by staging this stupid, worthless, ineffective, and unnecessary war on drugs.<br>
<br>
Recent reports say that he's wasted over 90 billion dollars on the &quot;war on drugs&quot; and he hasn't even been able to touch the problem! What'd he do, close the Canadian border?  Marijuana is a plant! You can't just expect that to stop the flow, when people can grow it in America!<br>
<br>
