<br>
Ashcroft's been spending all this time screwing people's lives, giving them arrest/criminal records, for puffing on a joint.  Now I'm not saying that drugs are a good idea, but decriminalization would be a better way to go, legalization would bring some defenite revenue to the government, but he either doesen't realize this, or he's in stubborn denial, and refuses to just give in.  Maybe he doesen't want to look &quot;soft&quot;, but that'd be better than making a mockery out of the nation, and wasting much-needed budget money out of taxpayer's pockets.<br>
<br>
